{"type":"text","timestamp":1775865549254,"sessionID":"ses_2862b54d6ffePl5qPuCQbuOsMI","part":{"id":"prt_d79d5b18e001zODKQKjJfpoYf6","messageID":"msg_d79d5a826001nFpe38Cidv53pO","sessionID":"ses_2862b54d6ffePl5qPuCQbuOsMI","type":"text","text":"## Verification Summary: AR-024 — DockerService封装\n\n### ✅ Tests\n- **125 tests passed** - All tests pass\n\n### ✅ Package Layout (Spec Compliance)\n\n| Spec Path | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| `pyproject.toml` | ✅ | Correct `kubectl-agentcube` script entry |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | ✅ | `__version__`, exports all runtimes & services |\n| `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | ✅ | Exports `app` |\n| `agentcube/cli/main.py` | ✅ | Typer app with `pack`, `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, `status` commands |\n| `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | ✅ | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\n| `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | ✅ | Re-exports all runtimes |\n| `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | ✅ | `PackRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | ✅ | `BuildRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | ✅ | `PublishRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | ✅ | `InvokeRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | ✅ | `StatusRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | ✅ | Services package docstring |\n| `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | ✅ | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` |\n| `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | ✅ | `DockerService` (AR-024) |\n| `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | ✅ | `KubernetesProvider` |\n| `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | ✅ | `AgentCubeProvider` |\n| `agentcube/operations/__init__.py` | ✅ | Placeholder module |\n| `examples/*` | ❌ | Not implemented (minor) |\n\n### ⚠️ Lint Issues (Non-blocking)\n- **UP045/UP006**: Using older `Optional[]` and `Dict[]` type annotations (Python 3.9 compatible)\n- **B904**: Exception chaining style warnings\n- **I001**: Import sorting (cosmetic)\n- **E501**: Line length warnings (minor)\n\nThese are stylistic issues, not functional bugs.\n\n### Conclusion\n**All functional requirements are met.** Tests pass. The `DockerService` is fully implemented per AR-024 spec with Dockerfile generation, Docker build, push, and image management capabilities.","time":{"start":1775865549252,"end":1775865549252}}}
